hackathon-rules:
Teams: 1-4 people
Submission Requirements: Participants must upload their projects to Devpost to be considered for an award. Their demo must consist of only the code that was submitted to Devpost. 
Submission Rights: Submissions can be displayed and used for promotional purposes in future PackHacks competitions.
